244
00:15:43,242 --> 00:15:43,936
There'd better be!

245
00:15:44,009 --> 00:15:44,907
We found him..

246
00:15:45,711 --> 00:15:46,439
Found who?

247
00:15:46,578 --> 00:15:47,510
The messiah!

248
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:48,937
Ha, ha, ha...

249
00:15:49,014 --> 00:15:50,481
